com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters

Class ProviderListenerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.avaya.jtapi.tsapi.adapters.ProviderListenerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.EventListener, ProviderListener
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    PrivateDataProviderListenerAdapter

    public abstract class ProviderListenerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements ProviderListener
    An adapter which is notified of all changes to the Provider object. The methods in this class are empty; this class is provided as a convenience for easily creating listeners by extending this class and overriding only the methods of interest.
    See Also:
    ProviderListener
